{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And this was one of the young men that were later caught escaping and hung.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I couldn't not cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We were taken again back to Auschwitz after two months because of the advancing Russian army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz, this time we knew what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we knew there was going to be a selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we knew what b-- bad condition we were in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So my mother was the weakest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "She's developed some kind of a fever every day, and she was very ill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I saw how Mengele then made the selections, and most of my cousins already were selected to go to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I saw that anybody had any kind of a paper bandage, which we used to cover our sores, would automatically go to the right side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I quickly tore off the bandage off my mother's leg, and I gave her a shove into her back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And she straightened out and she passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then I passed too, and my aunt who was always with us as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We passed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then we were taken again to the, to the baths.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we were shaven again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Our hair was shaven even though we had already about an inch of hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And then we were given our number tattooed on our-- on our arm, and-- which was kind of a hopeful sign that if we were given a tattoo, maybe we will be, again, taken somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We stayed six weeks in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We had many, many interesting events that happened to us in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I just want to tell you one that was very important.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I don't think I have time to describe Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I'm sure that it's well known.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
